			<article id="post-33" class="post-33 page type-page status-publish hentry">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">What is &#8220;gang stalking?&#8221;</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-431" src="https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/crows-on-wire-2-cropped.jpg?w=474" alt="crows on wire 2 cropped" srcset="https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/crows-on-wire-2-cropped.jpg?w=474 474w, https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/crows-on-wire-2-cropped.jpg?w=948 948w, https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/crows-on-wire-2-cropped.jpg?w=150 150w, https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/crows-on-wire-2-cropped.jpg?w=300 300w, https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/crows-on-wire-2-cropped.jpg?w=768 768w" sizes="(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px"   /></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/blue-line3.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-large wp-image-3942" src="https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/blue-line3.jpg?w=474&#038;h=10" alt="Blue Line" width="474" height="10" srcset="https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/blue-line3.jpg?w=474&amp;h=10 474w, https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/blue-line3.jpg?w=150&amp;h=3 150w, https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/blue-line3.jpg?w=300&amp;h=6 300w, https://fightgangstalking.files.wordpress.com/2013/05/blue-line3.jpg 698w" sizes="(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px" /></a></p>
<p align="center"><b><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><br />
<span style="color:#000000;text-decoration:underline;">Contents</span></span></b></p>
<p><a href="#firstintro">1.  A brief explanation of “gang stalking”</a><br />
<span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#secondintro">2.  America&#8217;s &#8220;deep state&#8221;</a><br />
</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#sectionone">3.  Crimes by U.S. law enforcement &amp; intelligence agencies</a><br />
</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#sectiontwo">4.  Oversight of law enforcement &amp; intelligence agencies</a><br />
</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><strong><a href="#publishednewsreports">5.  <span style="text-decoration:underline;">Published news reports</span></a> ***</strong><br />
</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#sectionfive">6.  History: <em>COINTELPRO, MKUltra, Red Squads, &amp; the Stasi</em></a><br />
<span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#sectionsix">7.  The national &amp; international scope of gang stalking</a><br />
</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#sectionseven">8.  Investigation, Surveillance, &amp; Harassment Tactics</a><br />
</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#sectioneight">9.  Mobbing &amp; workplace violence</a><br />
</span><span style="line-height:1.5;"><a href="#sectionnine">10.  Selection of targeted individuals</a><br />
</span><a style="line-height:1.5;" href="#sectionten">11.  The organizational structure of gang stalking<br />
</a><a style="line-height:1.5;" href="#sectiontwelve">12.  Social conformity &amp; obedience to authority</a><br />
<a style="line-height:1.5;" href="#sectionthirteen">13.  The U.S. Department of Justice (DOJ) &amp; gang stalking<br />
